data.text:
Dear families,

Welcome to La Follette High School, home of the Lancers! Our community is anchored by engaged staff and students who together take ownership of our school. Student voice is uplifted and centered to create collective ownership. We believe we are one, we are connected, in a school where all belong and all thrive.
